# Friday Tools Reference

These scripts live in `scripts/` or `skill-gateway/scripts/` and are callable from the agent or Cursor.

---

## Gmail (IMAP)

Script: `scripts/gmail.py`
Config in `.env`: `GMAIL_ADDRESS`, `GMAIL_APP_PWD` (16-char Google App Password, spaces OK)
Requirement: IMAP must be enabled in Gmail settings; Google Workspace domains need admin to enable IMAP.

```powershell
# List recent emails
python scripts/gmail.py list --count 10

# Unread only
python scripts/gmail.py unread --count 5

# Read a specific email by UID
python scripts/gmail.py read <UID>

# Search by subject keyword
python scripts/gmail.py search "invoice"
```

Output is JSON — pipe to Claude or parse fields: `uid`, `from`, `subject`, `date`, `body`.

**Agent usage:** When user says "check my email", "any unread?", "read email from X" — run the appropriate command and summarise the results in speech.

