## TTS — friday-speak.py

Script: `skill-gateway/scripts/friday-speak.py`
**ALWAYS run async / fire-and-forget. Never block.**

```powershell
# Bash (run_in_background: true) or append &
python skill-gateway/scripts/friday-speak.py "text to speak" &
```

Env overrides (optional, set inline):
- `FRIDAY_TTS_VOICE` — Edge TTS voice name (default: en-US-EmmaMultilingualNeural)
- **`FRIDAY_TTS_VOICE_BLOCK`** — comma-separated Edge voice ids **never** to use; see repo root **`CLAUDE.md`** — do not suggest or set blocked voices in `.env`, scripts, or docs.
- `FRIDAY_TTS_PRIORITY=1` — pre-empts ambient and competing TTS
- `FRIDAY_TTS_BYPASS_CURSOR_DEFER=true` — speak even when Cursor is focused

Falls back to Windows SAPI automatically if edge-tts network is unreachable.

