## WhatsApp (Evolution API)

Requires docker compose `--profile whatsapp` running.
API on `http://127.0.0.1:8181`, key in `EVOLUTION_API_KEY`.
Instance name in `EVOLUTION_INSTANCE` (default: openclaw).

Send a message:
```powershell
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8181/message/sendText/openclaw \
  -H "apikey: $EVOLUTION_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"number": "917870455443", "text": "Hello"}'
```

Allowlist (numbers that can send commands): `WHATSAPP_ALLOWED_NUMBERS`
Always-notify number (every Jarvis reply goes here): `WHATSAPP_NOTIFY_NUMBER`

