## Voice listen daemon

Script: `scripts/friday-listen.py`
Always-on mic → transcribes speech → POSTs to pc-agent `/voice/command` → speaks reply.
Start: `python scripts/friday-listen.py`

Ambient chatter: `scripts/friday-ambient.py` — fires every 60–120 seconds (after last TTS).

