## pc-agent endpoints

Base: `http://127.0.0.1:3847`

| Method | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| POST | `/task` | Run a Claude task (requires `X-Agent-Secret` header) |
| POST | `/voice/command` | Voice command (no auth, local only) |
| GET  | `/voice/ping` | Health / TTS provider info |
| GET  | `/voice/stream` | SSE stream of voice events |
| GET  | `/friday` | Web UI |

